        "subject": "LU-20178 lov: layout support for compression fields",
        "message": "LU-20178 lov: layout support for compression fields\n\nAdd LOV and LOD layer support for storing and retrieving\nper-component compression settings in composite layouts:\n\n- LOV: unpack compression type and chunk size from\n  lov_comp_md_entry_v1 into lsm_component_entry, and\n  repack them when converting back to on-disk format\n- LOD: propagate compression parameters through the\n  layout pipeline (lod_object.c, lod_qos.c, lod_lov.c)\n- Internal header updates to expose compression fields\n  in lov_stripe_md_entry\n\nSigned-off-by: Brian Barbisch <brbarbis@microsoft.com>\nTest-Parameters: Ignore\nChange-Id: I16c2885c915416ea200309f35eb5c7d1d54db18d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
